        "content": "<p>I came up with this: </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">f_asy</span>\n    <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">â„</span> <span class=\"bp\">â†’</span> <span class=\"n\">â„</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n    <span class=\"c1\">-- as x gets arbitrarily large the fuctions get arbitrarily close</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">filter.tendsto</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">Î»</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"bp\">|</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"bp\">-</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"n\">filter.at_top</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">ğ“</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>  <span class=\"bp\">âˆ§</span>\n    <span class=\"c1\">-- as x gets arbitrarily small the fuctions get arbitrarily close</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">filter.tendsto</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">Î»</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"bp\">|</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"bp\">-</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"n\">filter.at_bot</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">ğ“</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
